OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FVariable
OL,6,Fcloud and clear spells expected
OL,7,Fovernight, with a few patches of mist
OL,8,Fand fog developing by dawn and also
OL,9,Fperhaps a patchy rural frost. Winds
OL,10,Ffalling light.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTuesday:FAny morning fog patches soon
OL,13,Fclearing to mostly cloudy conditions,
OL,14,Falthough some sunny spells are likely
OL,15,Fto develop during the afternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
